snippet.title: Legions of Steel Tactics - Firing
snippet.description:
In this Short Tutorial, Agrippa Maxentius will show you some of the basic Fire Techniques you will need to employ against the Machines in our upcoming game Legions of Steel!

Official website: http://bit.ly/1LSGVWM
Release Date: July 16
